Subject: [PATCH] ARM: dts: imx6: skov: add pwm-regulator to control the panel's VCOM
Date:   Tue, 17 May 2022 09:18:14 +0200
Message-Id: <20220517071814.3626702-1-u.oelmann@pengutronix.de>
